{"tid":1514127,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不分藍黃。只有港人","createTime":"2019-08-28T15:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T15:21:35.000Z","uid":314144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6b686ee7bd7a41e3b383390943855f50fc6a7684","tid":1514127,"uid":314144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&ldquo;我&ldquo;同&ldquo;佢地&ldquo;唔同，所以行為都會唔同<br />\n而家啲示威者叫做後生仔， 勇武派， 有人叫我哋做曱甴 <br />\n普遍社會覺得全部同&ldquo;我&ldquo;無關<br />\n&ldquo;我&ldquo;係和理非，所以我只會遊行，其他社會運動唔關我事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係因為咁，我有一個大膽既想法<br />\n我地唔應該再分藍絲黃絲，只有係唔係&quot;香港人&quot;<br />\n<br />\n從最近「藍黃是政見 黑白是良知」一事睇到<br />\n大愛對班以自身利益為重既人根本就無用<br />\n佢地只會睇到眼前既利益到底有無受影響<br />\n<br />\n而依加班狗官一直都以&quot;香港人利益&quot;掛羊頭賣狗肉<br />\n令到班唔思考既藍絲以為政府真係一直都為佢地著想（唔排除有部分人係賣港）<br />\n然後不斷以示威者搞亂香港等等既用詞去令到班藍絲以為係事實<br />\n<br />\n所以從今日開始，我地要掛住&quot;香港人&quot;呢個名做任何文宣工作<br />\n然後再以高官有外國護照等等既事<br />\n說明依加管治既人唔係香港人<br />\n所以呢個政府根本唔係為香港人做事等等等<br />\n以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<br />\n以藍黃之分，佢地會認為佢地依然係香港人<br />\n但係當你直接咁話佢地唔係香港人<br />\n佢地既立場就會即刻收皮<br />\n同一時間<br />\n不分 和理勇武、富人窮人、老年後生<br />\n被分化既程度將會大大減少<br />\n<br />\n而香港人既定義好簡單<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">是不論是否在香港出生，不論何時來港，而是看你是否擁護香港的價值觀及文化背景</span></span></blockquote><br />\n香港人利益就係大義<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"8cc2b61ed008bd87f1b88dfaa71a8a4788afd0a6","tid":1514127,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:20:49.000Z","msg":"[置頂-連登改變世界]929全球集會抗赤納粹，召喚攬炒巴，G20巴，動畫巴，各文宣巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推上頂，文長但關乎出路麻煩大家耐心閱讀，香港人我地要一齊做<br />\n#Chinazi<br />\n#ProtectOurCountry<br />\n#StandwithHongKong<br />\n#NomadeinChina<br />\n<br />\n大家申請咗Twitter AC未，記得用新email注冊"},{"pid":"9ba4631a82f87256caa0777041c42d1c002a2bef","tid":1514127,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XiiQs9X.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiiQs9X.gif&h=b4bcc491&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTLKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=3569a0a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTLKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=5c69f508\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTLKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=ab6918cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"}]}